    "description": "Fake your own takeaway with the ultimate meatball marinara flatbreads. You'll top tangy tomato sauce with succulent handmade lean pork meatballs and melty mozzarella. Bake in the oven until oozy and irresistible, and serve with balsamic-dressed salad.",
